quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,By the snorting chargers
  100,2,"striking sparks [with their hooves]"
  100,3,"and racing [home] by morning"
  100,4,so they leave a trail of dust
  100,5,as they dash into the middle of the troops with it
  100,6,everyman is grudging towards his Lord
  100,7,"He himself [acts] as a witness to that"
  100,8,and is quite passionate in his love of wealth
  100,9,"Does he not realize that when whatever [lies] in graves is tumbled out"
  100,10,"and whatever is on [people´s] minds is checked up on"
  100,11,their Lord will be Informed about them on that day